* =============================================================================
* PCN 4-Layer Chip — Top-level SPICE netlist
* File:      pcn_chip_4layer.spice
* Config:    4 modules × 16 rows × 16 cols = 256 weights per module, 1024 total
*
* Hierarchy:
*   pcn_chip_4layer
*     bias_gen              — shared bias rails (vbias_n, vcm, vpi)
*     pcn_module_16x16 ×4   — mod0..mod3 (array + current_sub + precision_gate per row)
*     layer_link_16 ×3      — link_01, link_12, link_23
*
* Signal flow (vertical = layers, r = row index 0..15):
*
*   Module 0 (bottom):  raw_inp_r  → array → m0_iout_r
*   Link 01 ascending:  m0_iout_r  → source follower → m1_inp_r
*   Link 01 descending: m1_iout_r  → NMOS sink       → m0_pred_r
*   Module 1:           m1_inp_r   → array → m1_iout_r
*   Link 12 ascending:  m1_iout_r  → source follower → m2_inp_r
*   Link 12 descending: m2_iout_r  → NMOS sink       → m1_pred_r
*   Module 2:           m2_inp_r   → array → m2_iout_r
*   Link 23 ascending:  m2_iout_r  → source follower → m3_inp_r
*   Link 23 descending: m3_iout_r  → NMOS sink       → m2_pred_r
*   Module 3 (top):     m3_inp_r   → array → m3_iout_r  (chip output)
*
* Module port order (pcn_module_16x16):
*   [0..31]   inp_col_c inn_col_c  (16 differential column input pairs)
*   [32..47]  iout_row_r           (16 KCL bus outputs — exposed for layer_link)
*   [48..63]  i_pred_r             (16 prediction current inputs from layer above)
*   [64..79]  ierr_dig_r           (16 digital error flags → hebb_ctrl.ierr[r])
*   [80..95]  we_row_r             (16 Hebbian write enables ← hebb_ctrl.we_out[r])
*   [96..111] vpi_r                (16 precision threshold voltages)
*   [112..116] vbias_p vbias_n vcm vdd vss
*
* Digital interface:
*   Each module k has a companion RTL instance pcn_digital_top #(N_ROWS=16, N_COLS=16).
*   ierr_m{k}_r  → pcn_digital_top_{k}.ierr[r]
*   we_m{k}_r    ← pcn_digital_top_{k}.we_out[r]
*   DAC path (dac_addr/dac_data/dac_we → mac_cell.iwrite) handled in RTL only.
*
* Module 3 i_pred = vss: zero prediction → all activity = error → maximum
*   unsupervised learning at the top layer. For supervised operation, replace
*   vss with external feedback currents on the i_pred ports.
* =============================================================================

.title PCN 4-Layer 16x16 Chip

* ── Library includes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.include "pcn_mac_cell.spice"
.include "bias_gen.spice"
.include "pcn_array_16x16.spice"
.include "pcn_module_16x16.spice"
.include "layer_link.spice"

* ── Supply ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.param vdd_val=1.8
Vvdd vdd 0 DC {vdd_val}
Vvss vss 0 DC 0

* ── Shared bias generator ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
* vbias_n ≈ 0.6 V (tail current / source follower bias)
* vcm     ≈ 0.9 V (common-mode reference for all diff pairs)
* vpi     ≈ 0.65 V (precision threshold; shared across all rows/modules initially)
Xbias  vbias_n  vcm  vpi  vdd  vss  bias_gen

