* =============================================================================
* Layer link 0 → 1
* =============================================================================
* iout_lower = m0_iout (ascending source, driven by mod0)
* inp_upper  = m1_inp  (ascending destination, drives mod1 column inputs)
* i_pred     = m0_pred (descending destination, drives mod0 current_sub.i_pred)
* iout_upper = m1_iout (descending source; shared net with Xmod1.iout_row)
