* Module 3 — top layer, i_pred = vss (no layer above)
* =============================================================================
* m3_iout_r: chip output representation of the most abstract layer.
*   — drives Xlink_23 iout_upper (descending prediction to mod2)
*   — available as chip output ports for observation or inter-chip chaining
*   — to chain to a second chip, route m3_iout_r through ipred_out pad drivers
